description:
Formulated by The Organic Tea Project, this Wellness Tea pack includes three blends essential for a healthy mind, body and spirit.
 
This pack includes 3 x 50g packs of pyramid tea bags of blends including:
 
Breakfast: Our breakfast tea blend includes low-grown organic Assam black tea as the base with high-grown Nilgiri tea added to give it a mutli-dimensional flavour.
 
Darjeeling: Darjeeling comes from the Darjeeling district of West Bengal, India and is produced at the highest elevation in the world. The altitude creates a unique muscatel flavour and special aroma.
 
Earl Grey: Whole leaf Assam, organic oil from bergamot oranges and blue cornflowers creating a fragrant, citrus and smokey flavour.
name: The Organic Tea Project 3EACH
